:name: LiteX VexRiscv
:description: This script runs LiteX BIOS on VexRiscv CPU.

$name?="LiteX"

using sysbus
mach create $name
machine LoadPlatformDescription @platforms/cpus/litex_vexriscv.repl

$bin?=@http://antmicro.com/projects/renode/litex_zephyr.elf-s_331660-260af83eb5e49de4fde160001f7f4ea957f9ca8c

showAnalyzer sysbus.uart

macro reset
"""
    sysbus LoadELF $bin
"""

runMacro $reset


